'''[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会]]开幕式'''在2014年2月7日於[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]][[索契|索契]]的[[菲什特奧林匹克體育場|菲什特奧林匹克體育場]]舉行，由20時14分舉行至23時02分<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/10/30/sport/sochi-2014-venues-winter-olympics/|title=Sochi 2014: Winter Olympic venues|first=Inez|last=Torre|date=31 October 2013|accessdate=12 December 2013|publisher=CNN|archive-date=2013-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213101341/http://www.cnn.com/2013/10/30/sport/sochi-2014-venues-winter-olympics/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本屆運動會為國際奧會主席[[托馬斯·巴赫|托馬斯·巴赫]]任內的第一場冬奧和奧運開幕式。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://keepingscore.blogs.time.com/2014/02/06/sochi-olympics-opening-ceremony/|title=Everything You Need to Know About The Sochi Olympics Opening Ceremony|date=6 February 2014|work=Time|accessdate=7 February 2014|archive-date=2014-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140211151301/http://keepingscore.blogs.time.com/2014/02/06/sochi-olympics-opening-ceremony/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/winter-olympics/26066007|title=Russian city prepares for Olympic opening ceremony|date=6 February 2014|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=7 February 2014|archive-date=2014-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209094727/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/winter-olympics/26066007|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/winter-olympics/10623697/Sochi-opening-ceremony-live.html|title=Sochi opening ceremony: live|date=7 February 2014|work=Daily Telegraph|accessdate=7 February 2014|archive-date=2017-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170526102444/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/winter-olympics/10623697/Sochi-opening-ceremony-live.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

是次冬季奥林匹克運動會由[[俄羅斯總統|俄羅斯總統]][[普京|普京]]正式宣佈開幕，觀眾約有40,000人<ref>{{cite web |last=Dassanayake |first=Dion |url=http://www.express.co.uk/news/world/458578/Winter-Olympics-Opening-ceremony-for-Sochi-2014-kicks-off-with-a-bang |title=Winter Olympics: Opening ceremony for Sochi 2014 kicks off with a bang | World | News | Daily Express |publisher=Express.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2014-02-07 |archive-date=2014-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140207235530/http://www.express.co.uk/news/world/458578/Winter-Olympics-Opening-ceremony-for-Sochi-2014-kicks-off-with-a-bang |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 儀式上的表演主要是關於[[俄國歷史|俄國歷史]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.advocate.com/arts-entertainment/people/2013/08/06/22-russians-who-we-wont-let-vladimir-putin-forget-were-gay?page=full |title=22 Russians Who We Won't Let Vladimir Putin Forget Were LGBT |accessdate=2014-02-09 |archive-date=2014-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140317072548/http://www.advocate.com/arts-entertainment/people/2013/08/06/22-russians-who-we-wont-let-vladimir-putin-forget-were-gay?page=full |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.channel4.com/news/sochi-2014-lgbt-gay-russia-winter-olympics-tchaikovsky |title=Putin's pride? Six famous gay sons of Russia |accessdate=2014-02-09 |archive-date=2014-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222025220/http://www.channel4.com/news/sochi-2014-lgbt-gay-russia-winter-olympics-tchaikovsky |dead-url=no }}</ref>。开幕式上的音乐多为俄国、苏联音乐家，如[[柴可夫斯基|柴可夫斯基]]、[[鲍罗丁|鲍罗丁]]、[[斯特拉文斯基|斯特拉文斯基]]、[[哈恰图良|哈恰图良]]等。

